[b]3.[/b] When that whole code method finishes after the last bracket, paste this underneath the last bracket of that code. [code]if(itemUsed == 2366 && useWith == 2368){
       deleteItem(2366, getItemSlot(2366), 1);
       deleteItem(2368, getItemSlot(2368), 1);
       addItem(1187, 1);
